<li><i><a href="/wiki/Datura_stramonium" title="Datura stramonium">Datura stramonium</a></i> (syn. <i>Datura tatula</i>)<sup id="cite_ref-12" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-12" title=""><span>[</span>13<span>]</span></a></sup> - zǐ huā màn tuó luó (<a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E7%B4%AB" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:紫">紫</a><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E8%8A%B1" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:花">花</a><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E6%9B%BC" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:曼">曼</a><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E9%99%80" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:陀">陀</a><a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E8%90%9D" class="extiw" title="wiktionary:萝">萝</a>)</li>
